クラス MessageDispatcher<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.technion.ewolf.kbr.openkad.net.MessageDispatcher<A>
  • 型パラメータ:
    A - 

    public class MessageDispatcher<A>
extends java.lang.Object
    Handle all the messages different states. A request state: init -> sent -> response received -> callback invoked A message state: init -> expecting -> message received -> callback invoked -> back to expecting or end
